item.title: Msn autologin first script
item.dc:creator: @jhon jhon
item.description:
@jhon wrote:

Hey guys this is my first ever script ^^ with help from wixter
[scar]// yey i did it thx wixter for some help ^^
// all you have to do is type your email and pass into the script select the
// crosshair and drag to msn window (this is meant for windows messenger and
// msn (not live!) —Jhon—
program msnlogin;

Const
email = ‘emailhere’;
Password = ‘passwordhere’;

Var x,y : Integer;

Procedure email1;
Begin
if (getcolor(492, 209) =16777215) then
wait(500);
movemousesmooth(x,y)
wait(500);
clickmouse(x,y, true);
wait(500);
SendKeysSilent(email)
writeln(‘enterd email’);
end;

procedure password1;
Begin
if (getcolor(494, 250) =16777215) then
wait(500);
movemousesmooth(494, 250)
wait(500);
clickMouse(494, 250,true)
wait(500);
SendKeysSilent(password+chr(13));
writeln(‘enterd password’)
wait(1000);
end;

begin
email1;
password1;
end.[/scar]
Enjoy you lazy ppl
p.s. this is meant for windows messenger and msn (but not windows live messenger)
